{{!
    @template tool_fix_delete_modules/report_table

    The template displays several tables about one course_delete_module task.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * title string - The title of the report (including the adhoc task's taskid and related course module id(s)).
    * reporttables string - HTML tables related to the course_delete_module task.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "title": "course_modules taskid(4321) (cmid:5432, instanceid: 1342)",
        "reporttables": "<div class="report-table"><h4>...</h4><table> ....</table></div>",
    }
}}
<div class="fix-report">
    <h4>{{title}}</h4>
    {{{reporttables}}}
</div>
